1949;;Abandoned;;American;;Joseph M. Newman;;Dennis O'Keefe, Gale Storm, Jeff Chandler;;film noir;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abandoned_(1949_film);;After her sister goes missing in Los Angeles, a woman tries to find information about the disappearance at city hall. The police are not helpful, but she does get support from a local crime reporter. As the two investigate the disappearance together, they are led to a shady detective and a black-market baby ring.